{"tid":1917141,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"macbook air 死機","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T10:21:10.000Z","uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e34762abb58fbfe569f65e2fb1778a9f7ac931e","tid":1917141,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"2015 air, 前晚用完, 今朝忽然開唔到機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncheck 左以下<br />\n<br />\n1) 差電 port 無壞 <br />\n2) 火牛無壞<br />\n<br />\n已試<br />\n<br />\n1) 開底蓋斷電<br />\n2) reset smc (火牛燈有轉色)<br />\n3) reset nvram (無feel)<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過, 1係死 logic board , 1係死 ssd<br />\n<br />\n如果死logic board 就算數買過部<br />\n如果死 ssd 就 換ssd, 但係手上又無第2隻 apple ssd 試, 佢個濕鳩插頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下過晒保拎去天才吧, 檢查費要幾錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者有無可靠 3rd party 維修介紹  (最好係黃)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b6f2edda3baa19ba91403a51cc1d1b8ab44770","tid":1917141,"uid":156636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"應該燒咗粒電容 <br />\n搵下之前個整iPhone巴打 問下"}]}